\c 3
\s Kuverengwa kwavaRevhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino ndiwo marudzi aAroni naMozisi nomusi wakataura Jehovha nawo naMozisi pagomo reSinai:
\v 2 Ndiwo mazita avanakomana vaAroni: Wedangwe, Nadhabhi, tevere Abhihu naEreazari naltamari.
\v 3 Ndiwo mazita avanakomana vaAroni, vapristi vakazodzwa, vaakagadza kuti vashumire pabasa roupristi.
\v 4 Asi Nadhabhi naAbhihu vakafa pamberi paJehovha nguva yavakauisa moto usakafanira pamberi paJehovha murenje reSinai; vakange vasina vana; asi Ereazari naItamari vakashumira pabasa roupristi pamberi paAroni, baba vavo.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha akataura naMozisi akati,
\v 6 Swededza rudzi rwaRevhi, uvaise pamberi paAroni mupristi, kuti vamushumire.
\v 7 Vanofanira kumubatira iye, nokubatira ungano yose pamberi petende rokusangana, kuti vapedzise mabasa etabhenakeri.
\v 8 Vanofanira kuchengeta nhumbi dzose dzetende rokusangana, nokubatira vana vaIsraeri, kuti vapedzise mabasa etabhenakeri.
\v 9 Vanofanira kupa Aroni navanakomana vake vaRevhi; vakapiwa chose pakati pavana vaIsraeri.
\v 10 Asi Aroni navanakomana vake unofanira kuvagadza, kuti vabate basa roupristi hwavo; asina kufanira, usaswederapo, anofanira kuurawa.
\v 11 Jehovha akataura naMozisi,
\v 12 Tarira ini ndomene ndakatora vaRevhi pakati pavana vaIsraeri panzvimbo yamatangwe ose anotanga kuzarura chizvaro pakati pavana vaIsraeri; vaRevhi ndavangu;
\v 13 nokuti dangwe rose nderangu; musi wandakauraya dangwe rose panyika yeEgipita, ndakazvitsaurira dangwe rose pavaIsraeri, pavanhu napazvipfuwo; rinofanira kuva rangu; ndini Jehovha.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Jehovha akataura naMozisi murenje reSinai akati,
\v 15 Verenga vana vaRevhi nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo, nemhuri dzavo; unofanira kuverenga varume vose vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura.
\v 16 Ipapo Mozisi akavaverenga neshoko raJehovha sezvaakarairwa.
\p
\v 17 Ndivo vanakomana vaRevhi namazita avo: Geshoni, naKohati, naMerari.
\p
\v 18 Ndiwo mazita avanakomana vaGeshoni, nemhuri dzavo: Ribhini naShimei.
\v 19 Navanakomana vaKohati nemhuri dzavo: Amuramu naIzhari naHebhuroni naUzieri.
\v 20 Navanakomana vaMerari nemhuri dzavo: Mari naMushi. Ndidzo mhuri dzavaRevhi, nedzimba dzamadzibaba avo.
\p
\v 21 Geshoni ndiye teteguru wavaRibhini navaShimei, ndidzo mhuri dzavaGeshoni.
\v 22 Vakaverengwa kwavari, vari varume vose vakaverengwa vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura, vakasvika zviuru zvinomwe namazana mashanu.
\v 23 Mhuri dzavaGeshoni dzinofanira kudzika matende adzo shure kwetabhenakeri kumavirazuva.
\v 24 Eriasafi, mwanakomana waRaeri, ndiye anofanira kuva muchinda weimba yamadzibaba avaGeshoni.
\v 25 Vanakomana vaGeshoni vanofanira kuchengeta zvinhu izvi mutende rokusangana, tabhenakeri, netende, nechifukidzo chayo, nechidzitiro chomukova wetende rokusangana.
\v 26 Nezvirembedzwa zvoruvazhe, nechidzitiro chomukova woruvazhe, ruri patabhenakeri nokunhivi dzose dzeatari, namabote ayo, zvokubata mabasa ayo ose.
\p
\v 27 Kohati ndiye tateguru wavaAmuramu, navaIzhari, navaHebhuroni, navaUzieri; ndidzo mhuri. dzavaKohati.
\v 28 Varume vose vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura vakaverengwa vakasvika zviuru zvisere namazana matanhatu; ndivo vaibata mabasa paimba tsvene.
\v 29 Mhuri dzavanakomana vaKohati dzinofanira kudzika matende adzo kurutivi rwetebhenakeri nechenyasi
\v 30 Erizafani mwanakomana waUzieri, ndiye anofanira kuva muchinda weimba yamadzibaba emhuri dzavaKohati.
\v 31 Ivo vanofanira kuchengeta areka, netafura, nechigadziko chemwenje, nearitari, nenhumbi dzeimba tsvene, dzavanobata nadzo, nechidzitiro, namabasa ose ayo.
\v 32 Ereazari, mwanakomana waAroni mupristi, ndiye anofanira kuva muchinda wamachinda avaRevhi, iye anofanira kuva mutariri wavanobata mabasa paimba tsvene.
\p
\v 33 Merari ndiye teteguru wavaMari navaMushi; ndidzo mhuri dzaMerari.
\v 34 Vakaverengwa kwavari, ivo varume vose vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura, vakasvika zviuru zvitanhatu namazana maviri.
\v 35 Zurieri, mwanakomana waAbhihairi, ndiye anofanira kuva muchinda weimba yamadzibaba emhuri dzaMerari; ivo vanofanira kudzika matende avo kurutivi rwetabhenakeri nechokumusoro.
\v 36 Basa rakatarirwa vanakomana vaMerari nderokuchengeta matanda etabhenakeri, nembariro dzayo, nembiru dzayo, nezvigadziko zvadzo, nenhumbi dzayo dzose, namabasa ayo ose;
\v 37 nembiru dzaparuvazhe kunhivi dzose, nezvigadziko zvadzo, nembambo dzadzo, namabote adzo.
\v 38 Avo vanodzika matende avo pamberi petabhenakeri kumabvazuva pamberi petende rokusangana, kurutivi runobuda zuva, ndivo Mozisi naAroni navanakomana vake, vanobata basa renzvimbo tsvene, ndiro basa ravana vaIsraeri; asina kufanira anoswederapo anofanira kuurawa.
\v 39 Vose vakaverengwa vavaRevhi, vakaverengwa naMozisi naAroni sezvakarairwa naJehovha, nemhuri dzavo, varume vose vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri.
\p
\v 40 Zvino Jehovha akati kuna Mozisi, Verenga matangwe ose avarume avana vaIsraeri vomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura, ugonyora kuwanda kwamazita avo.
\v 41 Zvino unofanira kunditorera vaRevhi (ndini Jehovha) panzvimbo yamatangwe ose avana vaIsraeri, nemombe dzavaRevhi panzvimbo yavana vose vemhongora dzemombe dzavana vaIsraeri.
\v 42 Mozisi akaverenga matangwe ose avana vaIsraeri, sezvaakarairwa naJehovha.
\v 43 Namatangwe ose avarume namazita avanomwedzi umwe  navanopfuura vakaverengwa kwavari, vakasvika zviuru zvina makumi maviri nezviviri namazana maviri namakumi manomwe namatatu.
\v 44 Zvino Jehovha akataura naMozisi akati,
\v 45 Tora vaRevhi panzvimbo yamatangwe ose avana vaIsraeri, nemombe dzavaRevhi panzvimbo yemombe dzavo; nokuti vaRevhi ndavangu; ndini Jehovha.
\v 46 Zvino kuti udzikunure matangwe ana mazana maviri namakumi manomwe namatatu avana vaIsraeri, vanopfuura vaRevhi pakuwanda kwavo,
\v 47 unofanira kutora mashekeri mashanu kuno umwe  nomumwe; unofanira kuatora uchienzanisa neshekeri rapanzvimbo tsvene (shekeri rina magera makumi maviri).
\v 48 Zvino unofanira kupa Aroni navanakomana vake mari iyo yokudzikunura avo vakapfuura pakaverengwa pakati pavo.
\v 49 Mozisi akatora mari yokudzikunura kuna ivo vakange vakapfuura vakadzikunurwa navaRevhi;
\v 50 akatora mari iyi kumatangwe avana vaIsraeri, mashekeri ane chiuru chimwe namazana matatu namakumi matanhatu namashanu, achienzanisa neshekeri rapanzvimbo tsvene.
\v 51 Mozisi akapa Aroni navanakomana vake mari iyo yokudzikunura, seshoko raJehovha, sezvakarairwa Mozisi naJehovha.
